    <data key="d0">Peloton: Improved Customer Satisfaction and Engagement Powered by Real-Time Recommendations</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ym_Gz_zH7w8</data>
    <data key="d2">Powers recommendations for over 6.5M members. Combines real-time microservices on EKS with an offline EMR and EKS GPU-based training pipeline orchestrated by MWAA.</data>
    <data key="d3">data_ingestion, compute_intensive, interactive</data>
    <data key="d4">True</data>
